all-day.description: Indicates whether the event spans the entire day.
all-day.description_zh: 指示事件是否跨越一整天。

event.description: The event object associated with this calendar interval.
event.description_zh: 与此日历间隔关联的事件对象。

interval.description: The specific time interval this event is associated with.
interval.description_zh: 与此事件关联的特定时间间隔。

:interval-divisions.description: Number of subdivisions within the interval for this event.
:interval-divisions.description_zh: 此事件间隔内的细分数。

:interval-duration.description: Duration of the interval in which this event occurs, in minutes.
:interval-duration.description_zh: 发生此事件的时间间隔的持续时间（以分钟为单位）。

:interval-height.description: Height of the interval in the calendar view, in pixels.
:interval-height.description_zh: 日历视图中间隔的高度（以像素为单位）。
